=== Noun ===
'''ball''' (plural: [[balls]])

# Any roughly spherical object
# An object, generally spherical, used for playing games
# ''([[baseball]])'' A pitch which falls outside the strike zone
# ''([[pinball]])'' An opportunity to launch the ball into play
# ''([[mathematics]])'' The set of points in a [[metric space]] lying within a given distance (radius) of a given centre.
# ''(vulgar)'' A testicle

# A formal dance
# A fun time
#: ''I had a ball at that concert''

